Intune Deployment Steps (Simple Explanation):
Set up Intune subscription
➝ Get a license and activate Intune for your organization.
Add, configure, and protect apps
➝ Decide which apps users need and set protection rules for them.
Create compliance policies
➝ Define what a "secure" or "healthy" device looks like (e.g., must have a password).
Configure device settings
➝ Apply settings like Wi-Fi, VPN, encryption, etc., to devices.
Enroll devices
➝ Connect users' devices to Intune so they're managed and secured.
